{"sha": "1cf9be98cdc2d2753b11dd71d83c03c82897b006", "node_id": "C_kwDOAAsO6NoAKDFjZjliZTk4Y2RjMmQyNzUzYjExZGQ3MWQ4M2MwM2M4Mjg5N2IwMDY", "commit": {"author": {"name": "David Wood", "email": "david.wood@huawei.com", "date": "2022-07-21T15:19:22Z"}, "committer": {"name": "David Wood", "email": "david.wood@huawei.com", "date": "2022-09-07T12:54:51Z"}, "message": "ssa: implement `#[collapse_debuginfo]`\n\nDebuginfo line information for macro invocations are collapsed by\ndefault - line information are replaced by the line of the outermost\nexpansion site. Using `-Zdebug-macros` disables this behaviour.\n\nWhen the `collapse_debuginfo` feature is enabled, the default behaviour\nis reversed so that debuginfo is not collapsed by default. In addition,\nthe `#[collapse_debuginfo]` attribute is available and can be applied to\nmacro definitions which will then have their line information collapsed.\n\nSigned-off-by: David Wood <david.wood@huawei.com>", "tree": {"sha": "78a4a0a3e69d8b51ac56f578c8500c14bcfd6712", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/trees/78a4a0a3e69d8b51ac56f578c8500c14bcfd6712"}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/commits/1cf9be98cdc2d2753b11dd71d83c03c82897b006", "comment_count": 0, "verification": {"verified": false, "reason": "unsigned", "signature": null, "payload": null}}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/1cf9be98cdc2d2753b11dd71d83c03c82897b006", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/commit/1cf9be98cdc2d2753b11dd71d83c03c82897b006", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/1cf9be98cdc2d2753b11dd71d83c03c82897b006/comments", "author": {"login": "davidtwco", "id": 1295100, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjEyOTUxMDA=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1295100?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/davidtwco", "html_url": "https://github.com/davidtwco", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/davidtwco/followers", "